data.description: Turn key home that has been well maintained by the original owner.   This 3 bedroom home offers vaulted ceilings, spacious eat in kitchen, gas range, refrigerator, washer, dryer, white 2'' window coverings, beautiful window sills, garage sink, extra 220 volt outlet in garage, new garage door and newer exterior paint.  Master bedroom has a walk-in closet, chandelier light fixture and extra shelving.  Master bath has glass shower doors and dual basins.  North South facing home with a beautifully low maintenance back yard landscaping and covered patio.  2 car garage with side access door to rear yard.   Community offers a network of trails, parks and expanses grassy areas to enjoy.  Close to Banner Ironwood Medical Center, Fry's grocery store, and many other new shops and restaurants. Exterior gas connection for BBQ gas grill and 2 holiday light outlets with switches.  Home is a PowerWise home with SRP.  Great investment home with rental price range of $1693 to $1839 based on rentfax report which has been uploaded to the document section.
